  "description": "Axolotl Utils is a client-side Fabric mod designed to enhance the axolotl experience in Minecraft.",
  "body": "![AxolotlUtils](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/AxolotlUtils/refs/heads/main/README/minecraft_title.png)\n\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/fweigel-dev/AxolotlUtils\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/AxolotlUtils/refs/heads/main/README/github_icon_bg.png\" alt=\"GitHub\" style=\"margin: 5px 10px;\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/axolotlutils\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/AxolotlUtils/refs/heads/main/README/modrinth_icon_bg.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\" style=\"margin: 5px 10px;\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/axolotlutils\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/AxolotlUtils/refs/heads/main/README/curseforge_icon_bg.png\" alt=\"Curseforge\" style=\"margin: 5px 10px;\"></a>\n</p>\n\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 40px 0;\">\n  <div>\n    <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Supported Versions:</h3>\n    <img width=\"165\" height=\"84\" alt=\"Minecraft 1.21.11\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/AxolotlUtils/refs/heads/main/README/1.21.11.png\"/>\n    <img width=\"165\" height=\"84\" alt=\"Minecraft 26.1\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/AxolotlUtils/refs/heads/main/README/26.1.png\"/>\n    <img width=\"165\" height=\"84\" alt=\"Minecraft 26.2\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fweigel-dev/AxolotlUtils/refs/heads/main/README/26.2.png\"/>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\nAxolotl Utils is a client-side Fabric mod designed to enhance the axolotl experience in Minecraft. Whether you're hunting for the elusive blue axolotl or simply want better\nvisual feedback of the color of it in you bucket, this mod provides quality-of-life improvements that make working with axolotls more enjoyable and efficient.\n",
